Prima extension for OpenGL drawing.

Works on win32, cygwin and x11.

Dependencies:
    apt-get install libgl-dev

Optional dependencies:
    cpan OpenGL::Modern

Howto:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make 
    make test
    make install
    perl examples/icosahedron.pl

Whereto:
 
    http://github.com/dk/Prima-OpenGL

Dmitry Karasik, 2011
